"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?33/5/33876?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Weight loss treatments (Beyond the Basics)",
"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?9/37/9811?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Weight loss surgery (Beyond the Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
